## Governance
- Every task must own task.md, spec.md, and a review directory.
- State machine: draft -> planned -> red -> green -> in_review -> ready_to_merge -> done.
- ready_to_merge or done requires review pairs from round 001 through current_review_round.
- Auth/input/API tasks require security-reviewer. Web/browser tasks require e2e-runner.
